#Building regression model with initial chosen variables
base.model <- lm(log(shares) ~ Day.of.Week + Category + n_tokens_title + n_tokens_content +
                   num_hrefs + num_imgs + num_videos + average_token_length +
                   global_subjectivity + global_sentiment_polarity +
                   rate_positive_words + rate_negative_words +
                   title_subjectivity + title_subjectivity, data = data)
summary(base.model)
